data.description: Beautiful and spacious 4 BR, 3Bath ranch-style cottage. A true vacation retreat in a rustic, mountain setting. Secluded but right on the edge of Skytop with access to all its amenities. Open floor plan allows for large group to gather, while providing many spaces for more intimate grouplings. Very large bedrooms, suitable for plenty of guests. Eat-in Kitchen with generous counter space, Sunroom overlooks pool and mountain scenery, Huge Dining Room with native stone Fireplace, Large Family Room with Cathedral Ceiling, 2 Master Suites with Baths and large closets, Oversized Guest Bedroom with large closets and Storage space, Bedroom Loft with balcony and sky lights, Oversized front porch and back deck, Covered Party Pavilion and Heated Pool. Ceiling fans and zoned heating.
